ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of NORA M. DUKE of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of George Young.
